Package jdk.test.lib.hotspot.ir_framework

Enum Class CompLevel

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<CompLevel>
jdk.test.lib.hotspot.ir_framework.CompLevel
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<CompLevel>, Constable
public enum CompLevel extends Enum<CompLevel>
Compilation levels used by the framework. The compilation levels map to the used levels in HotSpot (apart from the framework specific values SKIP and WAIT_FOR_COMPILATION that cannot be found in HotSpot).

The compilation levels can be specified in the Test, ForceCompile and DontCompile annotation.

See Also:
Test, ForceCompile, DontCompile

  • Enum Constant Details

    • WAIT_FOR_COMPILATION

      public static final CompLevel WAIT_FOR_COMPILATION
      Can only be used at Test.compLevel(). After the warm-up, the framework keeps invoking the test over a span of 10s (configurable by setting the property flag -DWaitForCompilationTimeout) until HotSpot compiles the Test method. If the method was not compiled after 10s, an exception is thrown. The framework does not wait for the compilation if the test VM is run with -Xcomp, -XX:-UseCompiler or -DStressCC=true.

    • SKIP

      public static final CompLevel SKIP
      Can only be used at Test.compLevel(). Skip a compilation of the @Test method completely.

    • ANY

      public static final CompLevel ANY
      Use any compilation level depending on the usage:

      • @Test, @ForceCompile: Use the highest available compilation level which is usually C2.

      • @DontCompile: Prevents any compilation of the associated helper method.

    • C1

      public static final CompLevel C1
      Compilation level 1: C1 compilation without any profile information.

    • C1_LIMITED_PROFILE

      public static final CompLevel C1_LIMITED_PROFILE
      Compilation level 2: C1 compilation with limited profile information: Includes Invocation and backedge counters.

    • C1_FULL_PROFILE

      public static final CompLevel C1_FULL_PROFILE
      Compilation level 3: C1 compilation with full profile information: Includes Invocation and backedge counters with MDO.

    • C2

      public static final CompLevel C2
      Compilation level 4: C2 compilation with full optimizations.
